#: ../../home/kovid/work/calibre/manual/faq.rst:844
msgid ""
"The following programs have been reported to cause crashes in calibre: If "
"you are running any of these, close them before starting calibre, or "
"uninstall them: *RoboForm*, *Logitech SetPoint Settings*, *Constant Guard "
"Protection by Xfinity*, *Spybot*, *Killer Network Manager*, *Nahimic UI "
